---
description: No eslint-disable comments; no unused variables
alwaysApply: true
---

# ESLint standards

- Never add `eslint-disable-next-line`, `eslint-disable-line`, or block `eslint-disable` comments.
- Fix the underlying lint issue instead (rename, remove, use the value, refactor, or adjust types).
- Never leave unused variables, imports, or parameters. Remove them or use them; prefix with `_` only when the name is required by a signature and truly unused.
